# ============================================================================
# DEPRECATED — there is now ONE config file at the repo root.
#
# Use the root-level configuration instead:
#     cd ..        # repo root
#     cp .env.example .env
#     make keys    # interactive wizard to add API keys
#
# The backend reads the repo-root .env automatically (and backend/.env if it
# exists), so you no longer need to maintain a separate file here.
